My first map, has a few bugs. I was going to remake it but ill put my effort into a newer one.
To install place the file "fy_swim.bsp" into the folder ...\Steam\steamapps\username\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps. A nav file is included yet bots won't go into tunnels -_-. Hope you like it anyway xD.
